        "collapsible_tab_Lj4hdQ": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What makes xPillow different",
            "heading_size": "medium",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>xPillow is engineered with a precise 27° incline to support natural alignment, reduce strain, and make positioning effortless.</p><p>Small adjustment. Massive difference.</p><p>When your body feels supported, comfort increases, movement becomes easier, and connection happens naturally.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 18,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_BKMDBG": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Why couples choose xPillow",
            "heading_size": "medium",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>The firm supportive core keeps its shape and delivers consistent lift exactly where it’s needed — no awkward repositioning, no discomfort, no effort.</p><p>It helps support the hips and lower back while improving angles that feel more natural for both partners.</p><p>The result is a smoother, more comfortable experience that feels intuitive instead of forced.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 18,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_LNgMtk": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Designed for real life",
            "heading_size": "medium",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Made with premium memory foam and a soft removable cover, xPillow blends performance with a discreet design that fits naturally into your bedroom.</p><p>No complicated setup.<br/><br/>No learning curve.<br/><br/>Just better comfort instantly.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 18,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
