      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_row_dzExVy": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What if my partner thinks it's weird?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Most partners are amazed by the increased comfort and support. We focus on wellness and physical comfort first the intimacy benefits naturally follow. It's about removing barriers, not adding awkwardness.<br/><br/></p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_Di4Nqe": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What if i'm not satisfied with the results?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>We offer a 30 day satisfaction guarantee. If the pillow doesn't transform your comfort and experience as promised, return it for a full refund. We're that confident you'll love it.</p>",
