        },
        "collapsible_row_CHz9GQ": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do i clean maintain it?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Super easy! The premium cover is machine-washable, and the water-resistant core wipes clean easily. It's designed for regular use and maintains its shape wash after wash.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_RV98kE": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How is this different from regular pillows",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Regular pillows compress and lose shape under pressure. Our xPillow foam maintains perfect support even during dynamic movement, ensuring consistent angles every time.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_nGFegC": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Will this look obvious in my bedroom?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Absolutely not. We specifically designed it to complement bedroom décor with elegant aesthetics. Many customers use it as an accent pillow when not in use - no one knows its true purpose.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
